Payback my ass.

580
00:33:31,520 --> 00:33:32,200
That's right.

581
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:34,760
I am the murderer.

582
00:33:37,160 --> 00:33:38,240
You hear that clearly?

583
00:33:40,360 --> 00:33:42,480
But if you bully my daughter,

584
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:45,160
I'll take you down with me.

585
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:46,480
No!

586
00:34:09,360 --> 00:34:10,440
Oh my God!

587
00:34:11,080 --> 00:34:12,080
Someone's been killed!

588
00:34:12,640 --> 00:34:13,400
Murder!

589
00:34:13,400 --> 00:34:14,320
There's so much blood!

590
00:34:17,080 --> 00:34:18,160
Wu Huilian.

591
00:34:18,160 --> 00:34:18,920
Here.

592
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,120
Sit.

593
00:34:26,680 --> 00:34:28,360
How come it's you again?

594
00:34:28,600 --> 00:34:29,480
Yeah.

595
00:34:30,560 --> 00:34:31,840
Quite a coincidence.

596
00:34:32,080 --> 00:34:33,640
So what's it about this time?

597
00:34:34,120 --> 00:34:36,120
She... she tried to kill me!

598
00:34:36,120 --> 00:34:36,960
This is the weapon.

599
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:39,000
Have you no shame?

600
00:34:41,560 --> 00:34:44,160
You bastard, open your eyes and take a good look.

601
00:34:44,640 --> 00:34:46,440
It's my head that got hurt.

602
00:34:46,920 --> 00:34:49,240
Your fingerprints are all over this weapon.

603
00:34:50,040 --> 00:34:51,120
Officer, that's not it.

604
00:34:51,320 --> 00:34:51,920
She hit herself.

605
00:34:51,920 --> 00:34:52,720
It's got nothing to do with me.

606
00:34:53,040 --> 00:34:53,640
Officer.

607
00:34:53,640 --> 00:34:55,640
This guy stirred up a mob outside our shop.

608
00:34:55,640 --> 00:34:56,560
Lock him up.

609
00:34:56,560 --> 00:34:57,560
Don't you talk nonsense.

610
00:34:57,560 --> 00:34:58,640
You invaded my privacy first.

611
00:34:58,640 --> 00:34:59,440
What nonsense am I talking?

612
00:34:59,440 --> 00:35:00,640
You? Invade your privacy?

613
00:35:00,640 --> 00:35:01,520
You two.

614
00:35:01,520 --> 00:35:02,440
Stop arguing.

615
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:03,640
What privacy did we invade?

616
00:35:03,640 --> 00:35:05,160
Spell it out clearly.

617
00:35:05,640 --> 00:35:06,320
Go on.

618
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:07,080
Say it.

619
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:12,080
Actually, it's nothing really.

620
00:35:12,080 --> 00:35:13,240
Just a small family matter.

621
00:35:13,240 --> 00:35:15,680
How about we settle privately? Okay?

622
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:18,040
You want to settle privately?

623
00:35:18,840 --> 00:35:20,600
You change your tune faster than flipping a page.

624
00:35:20,840 --> 00:35:22,280
You think this is a small matter?

625
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:25,040
Have you no shame at all?

626
00:35:25,040 --> 00:35:26,880
What kind of scumbag are you?

627
00:35:28,040 --> 00:35:29,960
Officer, let me tell you what happened.

628
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:32,920
This man's wife was bedridden and sick,

629
00:35:33,440 --> 00:35:35,440
and he was out committing adultery.

630
00:35:35,920 --> 00:35:38,440
Then his wife passed away,

631
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:41,400
and he put on a fake show, throwing a big banquet.

632
00:35:41,680 --> 00:35:43,720
And at his own wife's funeral,

633
00:35:43,720 --> 00:35:46,320
he was flirting with that harlot.

634
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:48,080
Aren't you afraid of being struck by lightning?

635
00:35:48,080 --> 00:35:48,760
Scumbag.

636
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:50,840
Wait, this has nothing to do with you, right?

637
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:54,200
Shameless, absolutely shameless!

638
00:35:54,320 --> 00:35:56,080
You bastard, you're truly shameless!

639
00:35:56,240 --> 00:35:57,840
Your shady dealings

640
00:35:57,840 --> 00:35:59,120
have nothing to do with me.

641
00:35:59,120 --> 00:36:01,000
But you bullied my daughter,

642
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:02,360
and that I won't allow.

643
00:36:03,440 --> 00:36:04,560
Wu Huilian, will you ever stop?

644
00:36:04,560 --> 00:36:06,720
Since when is it your job to dish out justice at a police station?

645
00:36:07,840 --> 00:36:10,080
Li Yiran, I don't care.

646
00:36:10,560 --> 00:36:11,680
He bullied you,

647
00:36:11,800 --> 00:36:13,640
so I'll fight him to the very end.

648
00:36:13,640 --> 00:36:14,640
How are you going to fight?

649
00:36:16,120 --> 00:36:18,080
A life for a life again?

650
00:36:20,600 --> 00:36:22,560
My life's already ruined anyway.

651
00:36:22,600 --> 00:36:24,360
But no one gets to bully you.

652
00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:26,160
I'm not scared of going back to prison.

653
00:36:26,160 --> 00:36:26,960
I'll kill you!

654
00:36:26,960 --> 00:36:27,880
Enough!

655
00:36:29,440 --> 00:36:31,240
I don't care whether you go in or not.

656
00:36:31,240 --> 00:36:33,720
Wu Huilian, I don't care.

657
00:36:33,720 --> 00:36:35,440
Stop getting all sentimental about yourself.

658
00:36:37,680 --> 00:36:39,440
You think you're protecting me?

659
00:36:40,080 --> 00:36:41,640
You're hurting me.

660
00:36:41,640 --> 00:36:44,120
I don't want to face people pointing at me every day.

661
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:46,840
I don't want people saying my mom's a murderer.

662
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:49,400
I just want...

663
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:50,440
What do you want?

664
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:52,160
It's always about what you want.

665
00:36:52,160 --> 00:36:53,440
You do whatever you please.

666
00:36:53,440 --> 00:36:54,640
You're always this selfish.

667
00:36:54,640 --> 00:36:56,760
You're always so full of yourself.

668
00:36:57,240 --> 00:36:58,680
You do whatever you want.

669
00:36:58,680 --> 00:37:00,240
You vent your anger whenever you feel like it.

670
00:37:00,240 --> 00:37:01,640
What, stabbing one to death wasn't enough?

671
00:37:01,640 --> 00:37:03,080
Fine, I'll give you what you want.

672
00:37:03,080 --> 00:37:04,240
Don't go for him. Here, stab me.

673
00:37:04,240 --> 00:37:05,520
Come on, stab me!

674
00:37:05,520 --> 00:37:06,480
Stop fighting, stop it!

675
00:37:06,480 --> 00:37:07,840
He's right.

676
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:09,680
You're the one who got Pops killed.

677
00:37:12,520 --> 00:37:14,640
Did I get your Pops killed?

678
00:37:15,240 --> 00:37:16,840
Is that so? Say that again.

679
00:37:28,560 --> 00:37:29,360
Yeah

680
00:37:30,200 --> 00:37:32,200
I'm the one who got your Pops killed

681
00:37:33,360 --> 00:37:34,920
You're absolutely right

682
00:37:40,600 --> 00:37:41,600
Are you satisfied now?

683
00:37:46,640 --> 00:37:48,200
Wu Huilian

684
00:37:51,520 --> 00:37:53,760
You don't deserve to be a mother at all

685
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:57,280
I...

686
00:37:58,240 --> 00:37:59,160
Li Yiran

687
00:38:05,080 --> 00:38:06,160
Auntie Huilian

688
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:08,120
Please don't be upset

689
00:38:08,120 --> 00:38:10,160
Yiran only said that because she's furious

690
00:38:10,920 --> 00:38:11,760
It's fine

691
00:38:12,560 --> 00:38:13,440
I know

692
00:38:14,520 --> 00:38:15,800
She's as stubborn as a mule

693
00:38:16,600 --> 00:38:17,480
It's fine

694
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:22,760
Officer

695
00:38:23,920 --> 00:38:24,880
Do it his way

696
00:38:26,720 --> 00:38:28,320
Let's settle it privately

697
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:29,520
Fine

698
00:38:30,240 --> 00:38:31,440
A gentleman doesn't fight with a woman

699
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:32,640
Let's settle it privately

700
00:38:33,080 --> 00:38:34,440
Here, sign this

701
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:37,840
It's agreed

702
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:39,040
Your injuries have nothing to do with me

703
00:38:39,960 --> 00:38:40,880
Here, you sign too

704
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:11,520
Miss Li, it's been almost a week now.

705
00:39:11,520 --> 00:39:13,800
When are you gonna pay this month's rent?

706
00:39:17,400 --> 00:39:20,080
Sorry about that, landlady.

707
00:39:20,080 --> 00:39:22,320
Some family stuff came up and I forgot.

708
00:39:36,880 --> 00:39:37,920
Yiran

709
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:39,520
I really did like you back then.

710
00:39:40,160 --> 00:39:42,440
Yeah, cheating was my fault, I admit.

711
00:39:42,440 --> 00:39:43,520
And yeah, Linda is older than me.

712
00:39:43,520 --> 00:39:44,320
But you've got to understand,

713
00:39:44,320 --> 00:39:45,320
being with Linda

714
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:47,120
saves me at least ten years of grinding.

715
00:39:47,560 --> 00:39:48,960
Ten years, you get that?

716
00:39:51,200 --> 00:39:52,520
I came from the countryside.

717
00:39:53,000 --> 00:39:54,400
I clawed my way out with everything I had.

718
00:39:54,720 --> 00:39:56,120
You want me slaving away half my life

719
00:39:56,120 --> 00:39:57,400
just to end up farming back home?

720
00:39:59,320 --> 00:40:01,040
Yiran, I did the math.

721
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:03,200
This is two years of our dinners, dates,

722
00:40:03,200 --> 00:40:04,400
and shopping bills.

723
00:40:05,040 --> 00:40:05,960
Just to be fair about it,

724
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:06,920
let's split it down the middle.

725
00:40:07,600 --> 00:40:08,640
I'll knock off the loose change for you.

726
00:40:08,640 --> 00:40:10,160
Just send it to me on Alipay.

727
00:40:23,160 --> 00:40:24,360
social climber from the country

728
00:40:25,320 --> 00:40:27,120
Hope you stay a city dog your whole life

729
00:40:45,120 --> 00:40:46,360
What's up with her?

730
00:40:46,920 --> 00:40:48,080
Bad breakup or something?

731
00:40:48,080 --> 00:40:49,320
It's fine, keep eating.

732
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:58,640
I can tell you just got back.

733
00:40:59,200 --> 00:41:01,840
You picked the wrong hot pot spot.

734
00:41:08,160 --> 00:41:10,560
But I didn't think it'd be so bad you'd cry.

735
00:41:17,680 --> 00:41:19,120
It's... it's just too spicy.

736
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:21,640
Yeah, I can see that.

737
00:41:21,640 --> 00:41:23,760
So spicy it brought tears to your eyes.

738
00:41:29,240 --> 00:41:30,400
What are you doing here?

739
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:34,400
My dad's blood pressure spiked today.

740
00:41:34,400 --> 00:41:35,800
I went to the hospital to get his meds.

741
00:41:40,120 --> 00:41:41,520
About what happened today...

742
00:41:44,920 --> 00:41:46,120
I'm sorry.

743
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:49,640
Barely back and already causing you trouble.

744
00:41:50,160 --> 00:41:51,000
In the funeral business,

745
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:52,240
there's always trouble.

746
00:41:54,840 --> 00:41:55,880
That guy from today,

747
00:41:55,880 --> 00:41:57,560
he'll get what's coming to him.

748
00:41:58,720 --> 00:42:00,200
But don't take it to heart.

749
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:01,200
The way I see it,

750
00:42:01,200 --> 00:42:02,320
this is Xiaofang's fault.

751
00:42:02,600 --> 00:42:03,960
I mean, this should've been her job, right?

752
00:42:03,960 --> 00:42:06,240
Why'd she make you write it? Am I right?

753
00:42:06,240 --> 00:42:08,160
Worst case, just look it up online, you know.

754
00:42:08,160 --> 00:42:09,440
Why haven't you left yet?

755
00:42:11,120 --> 00:42:12,400
Aren't you taking your dad his meds?

756
00:42:15,360 --> 00:42:17,080
It's still raining.

757
00:42:18,680 --> 00:42:20,240
And I see you didn't bring an umbrella.

758
00:42:20,240 --> 00:42:21,520
I'll take you home in a bit.

759
00:42:28,640 --> 00:42:30,760
Eat, just keep eating.

760
00:42:30,760 --> 00:42:32,480
Don't mind me.

761
00:42:32,480 --> 00:42:33,840
Pretend I'm not even here.

762
00:43:21,440 --> 00:43:23,760
Mommy, thank you for today,

763
00:43:23,760 --> 00:43:25,600
for swimming with Yangyang.

764
00:43:25,600 --> 00:43:27,440
I wanna go again tomorrow.

765
00:43:28,480 --> 00:43:30,760
If you like it, Mommy will take you every day.

766
00:43:32,360 --> 00:43:36,960
Mommy, didn't you say water means wealth?

767
00:43:38,440 --> 00:43:40,160
I'm gonna catch all the wealth

768
00:43:40,160 --> 00:43:40,720
Hurry up!

769
00:43:40,720 --> 00:43:42,280
and bring it all home to us!

770
00:43:42,280 --> 00:43:43,040
Yangyang!

771
00:43:44,080 --> 00:43:46,440
You'll catch a cold in the rain, Yangyang!

772
00:43:47,040 --> 00:43:47,880
Come inside, quick!

773
00:43:48,520 --> 00:43:49,360
This child...

774
00:43:49,360 --> 00:43:53,400
I'm gonna earn lots and lots of money for Mommy!

775
00:43:54,120 --> 00:43:55,520
He was right.

776
00:43:55,520 --> 00:43:57,320
You're the one who got Pops killed.

777
00:43:59,800 --> 00:44:00,560
Yiran.

778
00:44:02,720 --> 00:44:03,800
Pops.

779
00:44:07,160 --> 00:44:09,760
You don't deserve to be a mother at all.

780
00:44:23,360 --> 00:44:24,360
Catching the fortune

781
00:44:24,360 --> 00:44:25,880
Slow down, Yangyang

782
00:44:26,560 --> 00:44:27,840
Slow down

783
00:44:27,840 --> 00:44:29,280
I want to catch

784
00:44:29,280 --> 00:44:29,880
Yangyang

785
00:44:29,880 --> 00:44:33,320
all the fortune and bring it home

786
00:44:34,320 --> 00:44:34,920
Come on

787
00:44:34,920 --> 00:44:35,840
Get inside

788
00:44:36,960 --> 00:44:38,040
You silly kid

789
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:41,000
You'll catch a cold, Yangyang

790
00:44:41,000 --> 00:44:41,840
Hurry inside

791
00:44:41,840 --> 00:44:46,840
I want to earn tons of money for you, Mom

792
00:44:47,440 --> 00:44:51,840
So you won't have to take on so much work

793
00:44:51,840 --> 00:44:54,240
Alright, Mom knows

794
00:44:55,680 --> 00:44:57,520
You're soaking wet all over

795
00:44:58,000 --> 00:44:58,760
Come on, let's go

796
00:44:58,760 --> 00:44:59,520
Let's go home, let's go home

797
00:45:45,560 --> 00:45:46,200
Hello

798
00:45:46,800 --> 00:45:47,440
Hello

799
00:45:48,360 --> 00:45:49,760
Yiran

800
00:45:49,760 --> 00:45:52,400
I heard about what happened with you two today

801
00:45:52,400 --> 00:45:54,680
Don't think I'm nagging you

802
00:45:54,680 --> 00:45:57,440
Your mom, she means well for you

803
00:45:58,160 --> 00:46:01,520
Don't say such hurtful things from now on

804
00:46:02,600 --> 00:46:05,880
Her heart's not made of stone, you know

805
00:46:07,480 --> 00:46:09,200
Uncle Daren

806
00:46:09,200 --> 00:46:10,080
Stop trying to talk me into it

807
00:46:10,080 --> 00:46:11,520
I know how to handle this

808
00:46:13,280 --> 00:46:14,280
It's raining pretty hard

809
00:46:14,280 --> 00:46:16,560
You're out working, so stay safe

810
00:46:17,640 --> 00:46:18,640
I'll hang up now

811
00:46:18,640 --> 00:46:20,480
Alright, alright

